{"type":"message","id":"82b3997c","parentId":"76f8cb55","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:38:48.191Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. If BOOTSTRAP.md exists in the provided Project Context, read it and follow its instructions first. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, July 7th, 2026 - 01:38 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-07-06 17:38 UTC"}],"timestamp":1783359528188}}
{"type":"message","id":"53d521db","parentId":"82b3997c","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:38:56.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me execute the session startup sequence by reading the required files.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_82b144dec72140fe95ecf4b1","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"MEMORY.md","lines":50}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_de1769c6362a471da2c6ba0d","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"~/self-improving/memory.md","lines":100}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2792495e498f4ab0b9cf9b68","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"~/proactivity/memory.md","lines":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":18424,"output":74,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783359528191,"responseId":"cht000daa00@dx19f3882e18b2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4ea5c9a","parentId":"53d521db","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:38:56.462Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_82b144dec72140fe95ecf4b1","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\\n\\n## 项目结构\\n\\n### 模块命名\\n- 小写+下划线：`stream_wasm.py`、`device_manager.py`\\n- 不用驼峰、不用大写\\n- 新模块放对应目录：stream→`src/stream/`，core→`src/core/`\\n\\n### 文件路径\\n- 主程序：`src/main/main.py`\\n- WebSocket代理：`src/stream/stream_wasm.py`（v7.60从main.py剥离）\\n- 前端页面：`src/web/index.html`\\n- 前端组件：`src/web/includes/console.html`\\n- 版本号：`src/main/constants.py`（唯一定义）\\n- 数据存储：`data/devices/{mac_clean}/`\\n\\n## UI调整规则\\n\\n### 尺寸用像素值\\n- 老板要求精确控制，不用百分比\\n- 例：信息窗体固定110px，不用70%\\n\\n## 执行纪律\\n\\n### 禁止大量调用进程\\n- 不要反复调用Python/PS进程\\n- 卡死系统=严重错误\\n- 专注完成任务，不盲目试错\\n\\n### 需求理解规则（v7.102教训）\\n\\n**遇到模糊需求时，必须立即停下来确认**\\n\\n1. **信息框/面板职责划分**\\n   - 多个信息框时，必须明确每个的具体职责\\n   - 问清楚：哪个显示关键事件？哪个显示详细日志？\\n   - 不要混淆职责\\n\\n2. **路径/目录结构设计**\\n   - 问清楚：这个目录未来会扩展吗？\\n   - 设置页面应该显示哪个层级？\\n   - 父级目录 = 通用类别，子级目录 = 具体类型/品牌\\n   - 例：SDK/（父级）→ HIK/大华/宇视/（子级品牌）\\n\\n3. **状态指示器设计**\\n   - 必须反映实际状态，不要硬编码\\n   - 问清楚：什么条件下显示什么状态？\\n   - 已连接时不显示\\\"等待连接\\\"\\n   - 已登录时不显示\\\"登录\\\"按钮\\n\\n[More content available. Use from=51 to continue.]\",\n  \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n  \"from\": 1,\n  \"lines\": 50,\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"nextFrom\": 51\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\n\n## 项目结构\n\n### 模块命名\n- 小写+下划线：`stream_wasm.py`、`device_manager.py`\n- 不用驼峰、不用大写\n- 新模块放对应目录：stream→`src/stream/`，core→`src/core/`\n\n### 文件路径\n- 主程序：`src/main/main.py`\n- WebSocket代理：`src/stream/stream_wasm.py`（v7.60从main.py剥离）\n- 前端页面：`src/web/index.html`\n- 前端组件：`src/web/includes/console.html`\n- 版本号：`src/main/constants.py`（唯一定义）\n- 数据存储：`data/devices/{mac_clean}/`\n\n## UI调整规则\n\n### 尺寸用像素值\n- 老板要求精确控制，不用百分比\n- 例：信息窗体固定110px，不用70%\n\n## 执行纪律\n\n### 禁止大量调用进程\n- 不要反复调用Python/PS进程\n- 卡死系统=严重错误\n- 专注完成任务，不盲目试错\n\n### 需求理解规则（v7.102教训）\n\n**遇到模糊需求时，必须立即停下来确认**\n\n1. **信息框/面板职责划分**\n   - 多个信息框时，必须明确每个的具体职责\n   - 问清楚：哪个显示关键事件？哪个显示详细日志？\n   - 不要混淆职责\n\n2. **路径/目录结构设计**\n   - 问清楚：这个目录未来会扩展吗？\n   - 设置页面应该显示哪个层级？\n   - 父级目录 = 通用类别，子级目录 = 具体类型/品牌\n   - 例：SDK/（父级）→ HIK/大华/宇视/（子级品牌）\n\n3. **状态指示器设计**\n   - 必须反映实际状态，不要硬编码\n   - 问清楚：什么条件下显示什么状态？\n   - 已连接时不显示\"等待连接\"\n   - 已登录时不显示\"登录\"按钮\n\n[More content available. Use from=51 to continue.]","path":"MEMORY.md","from":1,"lines":50,"truncated":true,"nextFrom":51},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783359536462}}
